    title: "Conversation – Making Friends & Small Talk",
    grammar: "<b>Making Friends & Small Talk (Haciendo Amigos)</b><br><br><b>Introducing yourself:</b><br>Mucho gusto / Encantado/a. (Nice to meet you.)<br>¿De dónde eres? (Where are you from?)<br>Soy de... (I'm from...)<br>¿A qué te dedicas? (What do you do for a living?)<br>Trabajo en / Soy + profesión (I work at / I am a...)<br><br><b>Small talk topics:</b><br>¿Te gusta...? (Do you like...?)<br>¿Qué te parece...? (What do you think of...?)<br>¿Has visto / probado / leído...?<br>(Have you seen / tried / read...?)<br>¿Qué haces en tu tiempo libre?<br>(What do you do in your free time?)<br><br><b>Showing interest:</b><br>¡No me digas! (You don't say!)<br>¡Qué interesante! (How interesting!)<br>¿En serio? (Really?)<br>Cuéntame más. (Tell me more.)<br><br><b>Making plans:</b><br>¿Quieres... + inf? (Do you want to...?)<br>¿Te gustaría... + inf? (Would you like to...?)<br>¿Qué tal si...? (How about...?)<br>Te / Lo / La + veo + día (See you on...)<br><br><b>Goodbyes:</b><br>Fue un placer. (It was a pleasure.)<br>Cuídate. (Take care.)<br>Hasta luego / pronto / la próxima.",
    vocab: { theme: "Small Talk", words: [{es:"mucho gusto",en:"nice to meet you"},{es:"encantado",en:"pleased to meet you"},{es:"¿de dónde eres?",en:"where are you from?"},{es:"¿a qué te dedicas?",en:"what do you do?"},{es:"el tiempo libre",en:"free time"},{es:"¿en serio?",en:"really?"},{es:"cuéntame",en:"tell me"},{es:"¡no me digas!",en:"you don't say!"},{es:"hasta luego",en:"see you later"},{es:"cuídate",en:"take care"}] },
